- (void) extractSeriesStudyImageNumbersFromFileName: (NSString *)  tempString  

Parses the fileName to get the Series/Study/Image numbers Used for files that don't have the information embedded such as TIFFs and jpegs In these cases the files are sorted based on the file name. Numbers at the end become the image number. The remainder of the file becomes the Series and Study ID
